   Al-Khateeb, Tahseen; Al-Naami, Khaled M.; Mustafa, Ahmad M.; Khan, Latifur, Univ Texas Dallas, Dept Comp Sci, Richardson, TX 75080 USA.
   Masud, Mohammad M.; Trabelsi, Zouheir, United Arab Emirates Univ, Coll Informat Technol, Al Ain, U Arab Emirates.
   Seker, Sadi Evren, Istanbul Medeniyet Univ, Dept Business, Istanbul, Turkey.
   Aggarwal, Charu, IBM TJ Watson Res Ctr, New York, NY 10598 USA.
   Han, Jiawei, Univ Illinois, Dept Comp Sci, Urbana, IL 61801 USA.},
