   Shi, Peng, Univ Glamorgan, Dept Comp \& Math Sci, Pontypridd CF37 1DL, M Glam, Wales.
   Shi, Peng, Victoria Univ, Sch Sci \& Engn, Melbourne, Vic 8001, Australia.},
