Affiliation = {Hu, BT (Corresponding Author), Zhejiang Univ, State Key Lab Fluid Power \& Mechatron Syst, Hangzhou 310027, Peoples R China.
   Feng, Yixiong; Wang, Tianyue; Hu, Bingtao; Yang, Chen; Tan, Jianrong, Zhejiang Univ, State Key Lab Fluid Power \& Mechatron Syst, Hangzhou 310027, Peoples R China.
